data.description: NEW PRICE!   Nestled in a gorgeous part of Greenville between Greenville and Travelers Rest with quick easy access to the Paris Mountain State Park. This home has four bedrooms, two and a half baths plus tasteful decor, and has been well maintained. This home has a spacious dining room, a two car garage and a lot of storage. Enjoy the large deck overlooking the private level back yard on the outside and on the inside hardwood floors, rock fireplace and open floor plan. Great family neighborhood to live in! Minutes to downtown Greenville, Cherrydale and Travelers Rest for shopping and restaurants. Call today for your appointment.
